# {% $markdoc.frontmatter.title %}

## Do you plan to continue support this project

yes we would like to continue supporting it, however not by us, we plan to move the project to the next generation of students to continue monitoring it and making changes as necessary

## Why did you built this project

we wanted a centralized place for all the information that are scattered everywhere, and as software and computer engineers this was our solution

## how was this documentation built

we used a fork of the famous stripe's documentation they just open sourced their documentation (may/15/2022) and they were a great fit for us
